<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | Assamese Text Annotation Tool</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Assamese&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Assamese', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 min-h-screen">

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between px-6 py-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <img src="/images/hero-img.png" alt="Logo" class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full shadow" />
                <span class="font-bold text-xl text-grey tracking-tight">Assamese Annotation</span>
            </div>
            <button data-collapse-toggle="navbar-default" type="button"
                class="inline-flex items-center p-2 w-10 h-10 justify-center text-blue-800 rounded-lg md:hidden hover:bg-blue-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
                aria-controls="navbar-default" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="sr-only">Open main menu</span>
                <i class="fas fa-bars text-2xl"></i>
            </button>
            <div class="hidden w-full md:block md:w-auto" id="navbar-default">
                <ul class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:space-x-8 font-medium">
                    <li><a href="/"
                            class="block py-2 px-4 text-[#1A1A1D] hover:text-blue-900 hover:underline transition">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/ner"
                            class="block py-2 px-4 text-[#1A1A1D] hover:text-blue-900 hover:underline transition">NER</a>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/coreference"
                            class="block py-2 px-4 text-[#1A1A1D] hover:text-blue-900 hover:underline transition">Coreference</a>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/about"
                            class="block py-2 px-4 text-[#1A1A1D] hover:text-blue-900 hover:underline transition">About</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>


    <!-- About Card -->
    <main class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[80vh] px-2">
        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl shadow-2xl mt-10 mb-10 p-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 text-center mb-6">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-blue-500 mr-2"></i>
                About this Tool
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
                The <span class="font-bold text-blue-700">Assamese Text Annotation Tool</span> is a comprehensive platform built to assist linguists, researchers, and developers in the annotation of Assamese-language texts. It supports both manual and AI-assisted tagging for various Natural Language Processing (NLP) tasks, making it easier to create high-quality datasets for training models.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
                The tool primarily focuses on <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700">Named Entity Recognition (NER)</span> and <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700">Coreference Resolution</span>, allowing users to identify and label entities such as names, places, and organizations. It also provides a user-friendly interface to manage annotations—add, modify, or delete them with ease—offering flexibility throughout the annotation process.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 mt-6 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fas fa-star text-yellow-400"></i> Key Features
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-none text-gray-700 text-base space-y-3 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-tag text-blue-500 mt-1"></i>
                    <span><b>NER Tagging:</b> Highlight words or phrases and assign categories like <em>PERSON</em>, <em>LOCATION</em>, or <em>LANGUAGE</em>.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-edit text-green-500 mt-1"></i>
                    <span><b>Annotation Management:</b> Edit or remove tags with intuitive controls.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-download text-indigo-500 mt-1"></i>
                    <span><b>Download Annotations:</b> Export your annotations in a structured format (e.g., JSON) for training or analysis.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-object-group text-pink-500 mt-1"></i>
                    <span><b>Coreference Clustering:</b> Group related mentions together and visualize relationships across sentences.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-robot text-purple-500 mt-1"></i>
                    <span><b>AI Assistance:</b> Use pre-trained models to auto-suggest entities for faster annotation.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-6">
                By streamlining the annotation workflow and supporting rich features tailored to the Assamese language, this tool plays a vital role in advancing regional NLP research and applications.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
                <a href="/ner" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-400 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-blue-500 transition flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Try NER Annotation
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/flowbite@latest/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
